Author: paperklipp
Text: My major binges tend to include a lot of protein, which feels like a cement block in my gut for like two days afterwards, it’s pretty unpleasant. Not to mention all the other hangover-like symptoms: dehydration, nausea, migraine, bloating, temperature disregulation. It’s not healthy but like two out three times I cave and take a lax just to speed things up.

Author: suika-smoothie
Text: Yeah I think I know what you mean. I've been dealing with stress by binging for like the last week and too exhausted to do anything but keep it down so I'm feeling this hard.
